A Toyota Hilux driver has crushed a commercial motorcyclist and his passenger to death at the Ozoro/Kw√†le expressway in Delta State. It was learned that the Toyota Hilux was at a very high speed when the brake failed, lost control, and hit the motorcycle from behind. Daily Post reports that the motorcyclist and his passenger died on the spot before sympathizers could come to their rescue. The driver of the Toyota Hilux was immediately arrested by the Police in Ozoro Division.